Class Attribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.objectmanager.data.DataObjectDescription

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DSTableFieldIFace

    public class Attribute
extends DataObjectDescription
implements DSTableFieldIFace
    This object represents an Attribute. A Attribute stores information about a scalar value that is used in a Step in the pipeline.
